StartGrid
=========

This project is based on the open-source project "Visual Bookmarks Chrome":
https://github.com/k-ivan/visual-bookmarks-chrome

Original author: Ivan Kuzmichov (k-ivan / ivan_k)
Original package license: ISC

StartGrid is independently developed and distributed. Its interface, visual
system, project identity, Chrome-only platform layer, icons, build pipeline,
storage namespaces, documentation, and release process have been rewritten or
substantially reworked for this standalone project.
